    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Key preventive maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis retains its hallmark precision with a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end. This vehicle offers a linear power band and exceptional throttle response, serving as a visceral driver's car that balances raw performance with structural integrity.",
